OL,3,CMan charged with murder after fatal St
OL,4,CPauls stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter another man was stabbed in
OL,8,FBristol earlier this week.
OL,10,FDavid Malcolm, aged 43 of St Marks
OL,11,FRoad in Easton, appeared at Bristol
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on 9 March.
OL,14,FThe incident happened on Ashley Road
OL,15,Fin St Pauls on Tuesday 5 March. The
OL,16,Fvictim has now been named as 30-year-
OL,17,Fold Aliki Mamwa, also known as Alex.
OL,19,FHe was taken to hospital and a post-
OL,20,Fmortem examination concluded he died
OL,21,Fof a stab wound.
