OL,6,FHis family have been updated and they
OL,7,Fare being supported by specially-
OL,8,Ftrained family liaison officers.
OL,10,FDet Ch Insp Phil Walker, the senior
OL,11,Finvestigating officer, said: "This is
OL,12,Fa significant step as we continue our
OL,13,Finvestigation into Alex's death and
OL,14,Four thoughts are with his family
OL,15,Ffollowing this news.
