OL,6,F"Enquiries, led by the Major Crime
OL,7,FInvestigation Team, remain ongoing and
OL,8,FI'd like to thank the St Pauls
OL,9,Fcommunity for their patience and
OL,10,Fsupport during these early stages of
OL,11,Fthe investigation.
OL,13,F"We are still keen to speak with
OL,14,Fanyone who was in the area of Ashley
OL,15,FRoad between 8pm and 8.30pm on Tuesday
OL,16,F5 March and has not yet come forward."
OL,18,FMalcolm has been remanded into custody
OL,19,Fand will appear at Bristol Crown Court
OL,20,Fon 11 March.
